---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AxionFlow - Engineering First. AI Second.">
	<nav class="border-b border-white/10 bg-[#0F1115]/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
				<img src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/img/logo-menor.png`} alt="AxionFlow" class="h-8 w-auto" />
				<span class="font-mono font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">AxionFlow</span>
			</div>
			
			<div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-white/60">
				<a href="#audit" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Audit</a>
				<a href="#architecture" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Architecture</a>
				<a href="#philosophy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Philosophy</a>
			</div>

			<div>
				<a href="mailto:kelvin.moraes117@gmail.com" class="bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-mono transition-colors">
					SYSTEM_CHECK
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main>
		<!-- HERO SECTION -->
		<section class="relative pt-32 pb-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0F1115]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="max-w-4xl">
					<div class="inline-block border border-[#3B82F6]/30 bg-[#3B82F6]/5 px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-xs font-mono text-[#3B82F6] tracking-wide">
						>> SYSTEM_STATUS: ONLINE
					</div>
					<h1 class="font-mono text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-8 text-white">
						Deterministic LLM Systems.<br/>
						<span class="text-white/40">For Enterprise.</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/60 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-12 font-light">
						We replace probabilistic guesswork with structural engineering. 
						<span class="text-white">Audit, Architecture, and Repair</span> for mission-critical AI pipelines.
					</p>

					<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
						<a href="mailto:kelvin.moraes117@gmail.com" class="bg-[#EAEAEA] hover:bg-white text-[#0F1115] px-8 py-4 font-mono font-bold text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-colors">
							[ INITIATE AUDIT ]
						</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev/AxionFlow" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono text-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-colors">
							View Engine Source ↗
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE THREAT (REALITY CHECK) -->
		<section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0A0C10]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="font-mono text-white/40 text-sm mb-12 uppercase tracking-wider">01 // The Risk Profile</div>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-white/10 border border-white/10">
					<!-- Card 1 -->
					<div class="bg-[#0F1115] p-10 hover:bg-[#13161C] transition-colors">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#F59E0B] text-xs mb-4">CRITICAL_FAILURE: BLACK_BOX</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono text-white">Liability Wrappers</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
							Most enterprise "AI" is just a wrapper around an API call you don't control. When it hallucinates in production, you have no audit trail, no replayability, and no legal defense.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Card 2 -->
					<div class="bg-[#0F1115] p-10 hover:bg-[#13161C] transition-colors">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#F59E0B] text-xs mb-4">CRITICAL_FAILURE: VELOCITY</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono text-white">Technical Debt Entropy</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
							Generated code without rigid AST validation is just accelerated technical debt. Your team is merging probabilistic bugs faster than your CI can catch them.
						</p>
					</div>

					<!-- Card 3 -->
					<div class="bg-[#0F1115] p-10 hover:bg-[#13161C] transition-colors">
						<div class="font-mono text-[#F59E0B] text-xs mb-4">CRITICAL_FAILURE: COMPLIANCE</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono text-white">Regulatory Exposure</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed text-sm">
							GDPR and EU AI Act require explainability. "The model did it" is not a valid root cause analysis for a regulated industry audit.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE MECHANISM (AXIONFLOW ENGINE) -->
		<section id="philosophy" class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0F1115]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="font-mono text-white/40 text-sm mb-12 uppercase tracking-wider">02 // The Mechanism</div>
				<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
					<div>
						<h2 class="font-mono text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
							Infrastructure,<br/><span class="text-white/40">Not Magic.</span>
						</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
							We don't sell prompt engineering. We implement <strong>Standardized Intelligence Pipelines</strong>.
							Every LLM interaction is encapsulated, typed, and structurally validated before it touches your codebase.
						</p>
						
						<div class="space-y-0 border-l border-white/10 ml-3">
							<div class="relative pl-8 pb-10">
								<div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#3B82F6] rounded-full"></div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono text-white">1. Static Analysis (AST)</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/50">We parse your codebase to generate a strict context graph, not a text dump.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="relative pl-8 pb-10">
								<div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#3B82F6] rounded-full"></div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono text-white">2. Deterministic Planning</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/50">The model generates a structured implementation plan (Markdown/JSON) for human review.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="relative pl-8 pb-10">
								<div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-[#3B82F6] rounded-full"></div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono text-white">3. Atomic Execution</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/50">Changes are applied as standard Unified Diffs. Zero hallucinated file paths.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="relative pl-8">
								<div class="absolute -left-[5px] top-2 w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
								<h4 class="font-bold mb-1 font-mono text-white">4. Validation Gate</h4>
								<p class="text-sm text-white/50">Mandatory build/test pass before commit. Broken code is automatically rejected.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Terminal Visual -->
					<div class="bg-[#0A0C10] border border-white/10 rounded-sm font-mono text-xs md:text-sm shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#13161C]">
							<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#FF5F56]"></div>
							<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#FFBD2E]"></div>
							<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#27C93F]"></div>
							<div class="ml-auto text-white/30">axion-cli — 80x24</div>
						</div>
						<div class="p-6 space-y-2 font-mono">
							<div class="text-white/50">$ axion audit --strict</div>
							<div class="text-[#3B82F6]">> Initializing Structural Analysis...</div>
							<div class="text-white/70">[INFO] AST Context loaded: 14,203 nodes</div>
							<div class="text-white/70">[INFO] Vector DB connection: ESTABLISHED</div>
							<div class="text-[#F59E0B]">[WARN] Non-deterministic pattern detected in /src/utils/ai.ts:42</div>
							<div class="text-white/70">       > Reason: Unbounded context window in API call</div>
							<div class="text-white/50">$ axion fix --target /src/utils/ai.ts</div>
							<div class="text-[#3B82F6]">> Generating deterministic context wrapper...</div>
							<div class="text-green-500">[SUCCESS] Patch applied. Tests passed (4/4).</div>
							<div class="animate-pulse text-[#3B82F6]">_</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- TECHNICAL LEADERSHIP -->
		<section class="py-24 px-6 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#0F1115]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="font-mono text-white/40 text-sm mb-12 uppercase tracking-wider">03 // Technical Ownership</div>
				<div class="max-w-4xl border-l-4 border-[#3B82F6] pl-8 md:pl-12 py-2">
					<h2 class="font-mono text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
						"I do not deploy hope.<br/>I deploy verified code."
					</h2>
					<p class="text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						AxionFlow exists because I refused to let stochastic models degrade my production environments. 
						I designed this engine to satisfy the most paranoid engineering standards: <strong>mine</strong>.
					</p>
					<p class="text-base text-white/60 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl">
						When you engage with AxionFlow, you are not hiring a chatbot wrapper agency. 
						You are hiring a Principal Architect who assumes personal technical responsibility for the stability, security, and determinism of your AI infrastructure.
					</p>
					
					<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 pt-4 border-t border-white/5">
						<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
							<div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#3B82F6]/10 border border-[#3B82F6]/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-bold text-[#3B82F6] text-xl">
								K
							</div>
							<div>
								<div class="font-mono font-bold text-white tracking-wide">Kelvin Moraes</div>
								<div class="text-sm text-white/40 font-mono">Principal Engineer & Architect</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-6 text-sm font-mono text-[#3B82F6]">
							<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev" target="_blank" class="hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">GITHUB_PROFILE ↗</a>
							<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kelvin-moraes-1620043a4/" target="_blank" class="hover:underline flex items-center gap-1">LINKEDIN_PROFILE ↗</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- OFFERING (SERVICES) -->
		<section id="services" class="py-24 px-6 bg-[#0A0C10]">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="font-mono text-white/40 text-sm mb-12 uppercase tracking-wider">04 // Engagement Models</div>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
					<!-- Service 1 -->
					<div class="border border-white/10 bg-[#0F1115] p-10 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
						<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
							<svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2L2 12l10 10 10-10L12 2zm0 18l-8-8 8-8 8 8-8 8z"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] text-xs mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">>>> SERVICE_ID: AUDIT_CORE</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono text-white">Production Risk Audit</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm h-16">
							A forensic analysis of your current LLM stack. We identify non-deterministic paths, security holes, and "magic" prompt dependencies.
						</p>
						<div class="bg-black/40 border border-white/5 p-4 mb-8">
							<div class="text-xs font-mono text-white/40 mb-2 uppercase">Deliverables</div>
							<ul class="space-y-2 font-mono text-xs text-white/70">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">></span> Traceability Matrix (Source -> Output)</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">></span> Vulnerability Report (Injection/Leakage)</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">></span> Refactoring Plan for Determinism</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Service 2 -->
					<div class="border border-white/10 bg-[#0F1115] p-10 hover:border-[#3B82F6]/50 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
						<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
							<svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"/></svg>
						</div>
						<div class="font-mono text-[#3B82F6] text-xs mb-6 tracking-widest uppercase">>>> SERVICE_ID: ARCH_SYSTEM</div>
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 font-mono text-white">Pipeline Architecture</h3>
						<p class="text-white/60 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm h-16">
							End-to-end design and implementation of a self-healing, locally-runnable AI orchestration layer utilizing the AxionFlow engine.
						</p>
						<div class="bg-black/40 border border-white/5 p-4 mb-8">
							<div class="text-xs font-mono text-white/40 mb-2 uppercase">Deliverables</div>
							<ul class="space-y-2 font-mono text-xs text-white/70">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">></span> Containerized Orchestration Engine</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">></span> Custom CLI Tooling for your Team</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#3B82F6]">></span> CI/CD Integration & Test Suites</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- FOOTER CTA -->
		<section class="py-32 px-6 border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0F1115] text-center">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-mono text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-white tracking-tight">System Stability Required?</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-white/40 mb-12 font-light">
					If you are ready to treat AI as a deterministic system component rather than a magic box, we should talk.
				</p>
				<a href="mailto:kelvin.moraes117@gmail.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-5 bg-[#3B82F6] hover:bg-[#2563EB] text-white font-mono font-bold text-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/20">
					INITIATE_CONTACT()
				</a>
				<div class="mt-8 font-mono text-sm text-white/30">
					Direct Line to Engineering: <a href="mailto:kelvin.moraes117@gmail.com" class="text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors">kelvin.moraes117@gmail.com</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-white/5 bg-[#0A0C10] text-xs font-mono text-white/30">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
				<div class="w-4 h-4 bg-white/10 rounded-sm"></div>
				<span class="font-bold text-white/50">AXIONFLOW SYSTEM</span>
				<span>:: V1.0.0</span>
			</div>
			<div class="flex gap-8">
				<a href="https://github.com/KerubinDev/AxionFlow" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">SOURCE_CODE</a>
				<a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">LEGAL_NOTICE</a>
				<a href="mailto:kelvin.moraes117@gmail.com" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">CONTACT_CHANNEL</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>
